{
  "id": "9d1483d65aa46938",
  "fields": {
    "apply_url": "https://jobs.ashbyhq.com/skelar/97b999ec-dada-4d39-adfe-aa7965a05f41/application",
    "company": "skelar",
    "compensation": "",
    "content_hash": "9d1483d65aa46938",
    "department": "Analytics",
    "description": "[https://app.ashbyhq.com/api/images/user-content/586ac3cb-f234-40cf-96fd-3daae8c41309/3a2721ac-0cf6-4bb5-a785-483b8d1018c3/Ashby_header.png]\n\nSKELAR is a venture builder that creates international IT companies according to venture capital investment guidelines. Together with our co-founders, we assemble solid and efficient teams to launch tech businesses that will succeed globally.\n\nWe’re looking for an Analytics Lead/Head for our partner company, Duomo.\n\nDuomo is building a platform for spiritual growth grounded in Christian values. It is modernizing the way over 2+ billion Christians worldwide connect with their faith.\n\nSome key facts about Duomo:\n\n - 300k+ users worldwide;\n\n - Users from 40+ countries;\n\n - 4.8 average rating on the App Store and Trustpilot.\n\nDuomo’s mission is ambitious — to make as many people around the world happier, wiser, and kinder, and to build the #1 Christian tech company.\n\nWhat is important for us?\n\n - Expertise in Tableau (or another data visualization tool)\n\n - Strong experience with SQL and Python\n\n - Previous experience on Leadership positions\n\n - Diverse analytics experience: product, marketing, business, etc.\n\n - Business-oriented mindset\n\n - Willingness to be a hands-on manager as well as the strongest analyst in the company\n\nWhat to expect from the position?\n\n - Direct impact on the business and its growth\n\n - Working directly with the CEO and play as a key analytics partner\n\n - Ability to to expand and scale the team\n\n - Building analytics for the most challenging periods and cases\n\n - Team management, including hiring new teammates\n\nWhat we offer:\n\n— Work alongside sharp, results-oriented teammates;\n— An opportunity to build a fast-growing career in a young company;\n— A strong, results-driven team;\n— A culture that values efficiency and common sense in decision-making;\n— Learning and development: mentorship from senior professionals, internal academies, 13 professional communities (including a marketing one), and participation in external courses and events.\n\nLet’s build the next big everything together!\n\n[https://app.ashbyhq.com/api/images/user-content/586ac3cb-f234-40cf-96fd-3daae8c41309/bf8afb62-59f5-436b-b500-74f06bd0bb6e/Ashby_footer_eng.png]",
